alls with fund managers analysts and economists are part of our process we make onsite visits to fund companies across the country to assess them on their home ground our portfolio managers meet daily to discuss our research and to evaluate risks and opportunities portfolio management we monitor and rebalance portfolios on a regular basis we will also make tactical adjustments based on our own assessment of investment opportunities under or over valued asset classes and potential risks read more tax considerations and longer term planning are an additional aspect of our portfolio management retirement planning for many clients retirement planning comes with a host of unique concerns the timing of leaving the workforce and taking social security increased longevity rising healthcare costs adequate savings sufficient income – all influence the decision of when and how to retire read more we work closely with clients to examine all available options we then create a strategy for success and see the client through implementation and maintenance of their customized retirement solutions from opening an individual retirement account to advice on setting up a combination kdefined benefit plan for your business longview provides solutions and guidance in planning for the years to come reporting we believe that open and clear communication is integral to the success of our relationships to that end we produce indepth portfolio performance reports quarterly letters and topical alerts as well as ongoing updates of our outlook on our website read more a dedicated primary advisor is accessible to you at all times we encourage regular face to face client meetings and are happy to meet in our offices or wherever is most convenient should you have questions or concerns we encourage clients to call or email us coaching longview provides comprehensive financial counsel we help clients avoid the financial mistakes and missteps that often come from emotional responses to market behavior or unsettling life events read more we work with our clients to help them stick to their investment plan and take advantage of favorable circumstances when they arise our clients draw on our collective seventyplus years of experience and benefit from sound advice whether life throws them a curveball or a windfall estate planning we help clients take care of the people and the organizations that are the most important to them for clients who wish to leave a legacy longview works closely with other trusted advisors such as attorneys and cpas read more we can guide you through the creation of wills trusts and medical directives we engage in planning for traditional nontraditional and special needs families we will help you craft a charitable giving strategy that benefits your preferred religious organizations educational institutions nonprofit entities and your community administrative services our client services manager will help you with account setup and maintenance withdrawals transfers wires and online access our custodian charles schwab also offers checking accounts debit cards and automated required minimum distributions read more our goal is to offer seamless administration of your accounts educator retirement services longview educator retirement services offers schools and colleges a range of comprehensive b retirement solutions we help schools fulfill their legal responsibilities to their employees by offering plans with low fees competitive fund performance best enrollment practices and ease of use read more unlike many firms longview assumes full fiduciary responsibility for all plans in addition we provide individual counseling to plan participants to help ensure they reach their retirement goals “do not seek to follow in the footsteps of the wise seek what they sought” — matsuo basho   personalized wealth management   financial planning portfolio design socially responsible investing investment management coaching retirement planning legacy   educator 