ur capital a division of td wealth private investment counsel  she also has experience in back office and custodial operations in her roles as a team manager and account manager at td waterhouse canada inc institutional services denise graduated from seneca college in business administration and has a post graduate in human resources management in her spare time denise enjoys spending time with her four children family and friends  she also likes to read and do numerical puzzles and crosswords dfernandeslongviewassetscom connect on linkedin close x tom lace cfa cpa ca partner member investment committee   as a member of longview’s investment committee tom shares responsibility for the firm’s investment decisions in addition along with alvin and james tom is responsible for undertaking primary research on companies in the longview portfolio and other potential investments prior to joining longview tom was a senior associate at pricewaterhousecoopers pwc in their audit practice where he focused on clients in the banking brokering insurance and technology sectors  while at pwc tom earned his cpa ca designation  he is also a cfa charterholder tom is a graduate of the university of notre dame where he graduated cum laude with a degree in business administration majoring in accounting and sociology  tom also graduated with beta alpha psi and phi kappa delta distinctions and a certificate in asia pacific business beyond longview tom is the founder of the horizons high school program  in his spare time tom enjoys reading travelling numerous sports and spending time with family and friends tlacelongviewassetscom connect on linkedin close x alvin lau cfa partner member investment committee as a member of longview’s investment committee alvin shares responsibility for the firm’s investment decisions in addition along with james and tom alvin is responsible for undertaking primary research on companies in the longview portfolio and other potential investments prior to joining longview alvin was a manager at cibc leveraged finance where he focused on structuring debt financing for midmarket private equity clients and corporate clients in this capacity one of his primary responsibilities was to analyze and value companies across a broad range of industries alvin is a cfa charterholder he received an honours business administration degree with distinction from the richard ivey school of business at the university of western ontario he is a passionate value investor who makes a practice of attending the berkshire hathaway annual shareholder meeting in omaha when not researching investment ideas alvin enjoys spending time with his wife and young son as well as playing ultimate frisbee and soccer alaulongviewassetscom connect on linkedin close x rb biff matthews chairman of longview member investment committee in addition to participating actively in the firm’s investment decisions as a member of longview’s investment committee biff along with doug and emily enjoys interacting with longview’s clients biff is a graduate of the university of toronto and oxford university and has studied and written about what works in investing for more than  years after practising law in toronto most recently as a partner of mccarthy tetrault biff acted as president of manitou investment management for  years before starting longview biff is a past chairman of world wildlife fund canada and outward bound ontario he serves on the board of el financial corporation when not working biff enjoys reading widely travel golf and spending time in the country with his wife sue and their adult children bmatthewslongviewassetscom connect on linkedin close x doug mccutcheon president of longview chairman investment committee doug chairs longview’s investment committee which is responsible for all of the firm’s investment decisions in addition along with biff and emily doug enjoys interacting with longview’s clients doug has been an investor in public and private companies around the world for more than  years prior to joining longview doug was an investment banker for  years primarily based in london england most recently doug was managing director and head of healthcare investment banking in europe the middle east and asia at ubs having started his career at sg warburg  co ltd a predecessor firm of ubs doug is a graduate of queen’s university bachelor of commerce he currently serves on the boards of the sterling hall school chairman and worldwide healthcare trust plc in addition to investing doug enjoys spending time with his wife deborah and their three children as well as participating in various sports and the arts  his philanthropic passions are healthcare and education dmccutcheonlongviewassetscom connect on linkedin close x emily won cfa cpa ca partner member investment committee as a member of longview’s investment committee emily shares responsibility for the firm’s investment decisions in addition along with biff and doug she enjoys interacting with longview’s clients prior to joining longview emily was an executive director in institutional equity sales at cibc world markets and merrill lynch  before that she worked in equity research at merrill lynch and td securities emily earned her bachelor of business administration from the schulich school of business as well as her chartered accountancy ca cpa designation with arthur andersen she is also a cfa® charterholder emily is a member of the cfa society toronto and previously served on the cfa society toronto equity committee and the national ballet school foundation board  she is a past executive member of the havergal college parents association when not being kept busy by their two young daughters emily and her husband andrew enjoy discovering new restaurants and travelling ewonlongviewassetscom contact us we would be pleased to speak with you we invite you to contact us at  or by email with any inquiries or to arrange a confidential meeting to discuss your investment needs